% =============================================================
% SECTION C  Bars 17–24: Reprise, climax, stretto, final close
% =============================================================
%
% BAR 17 G with ascending bass G–B–D–F#. Call-and-response.
%   S1/B1 outer-voice call. Inner voices fill.
%   A1: D4 D4 E4 D4 (source D D D raised). A2: B3 B3 C4 B3.
%   T1 concert: D4 D4 C4 B3. Written: d' d' c' b. T2: B3 B3 A3 G3. Written: b b a g.
%   Bar: E2 D2 F#2 A2 — D2 < E2; use E2 instead. B1: G2 B2 D2 F#2.
%
[V:1] b  b  a  a  |
[V:2] g  g  f  f  |
[V:3] d  d  e  d  |
[V:4] B  B  c  B  |
[V:5] d' d' c' b  |
[V:6] b  b  a  g  |
[V:7] E, E, F, A, |
[V:8] G, B, D, F, |
