% BAR 18 G major with passing motion. Voices weave.
%   A1: D4 C4 B3 C4 (source D C B C raised from D3/C3/B3).
%   A2: G3 F#3 E3 F#3 (independent inner line, all > D3).
%   T1 concert: D4 C4 B3 C4. Written: d' c' b c'. T2: B3 A3 G3 A3. Written: b a g a.
%   Bar: B2 A2 G2 A2. B1: G2 A2 B2 A2 (source G, A, B, A,).
