%   A1: B3 B3 C4 D4 (source B B C D raised from B3 area — B3>F3 ok).
%   A2: G3 G3 A3 B3 (3rd below A1; all > D3 ok).
%   T1 concert: D4 D4 E4 F#4. Written: d' d' e' f'. T2: B3 B3 C4 D4. Written: b b c' d'.
%   Bar: F#2 F#2 F#2 F#2 (hold over D pedal). B1: D2 D2 D2 D2.
